 Doyin Hassan and his late wife Bolanle Hassan Veteran Gospel actor, Evangelist Doyin Hassan has reportedly lost his lovely wife, Bolanle. Evang. Bolanle who is also a movie producer and Actor was married to Dr. Doyin Hassan many years ago. She died at the age of 57. She reportedly died on Wednesday 9th of December 2020. Report has it that she went to the hospital for a check up and complications arose. The death was unexpected. A service of song will be conducted for her on 17th December, 2020 at RCCG House of Favour in Redemption camp by 4pm while Funeral service takes place at same venue on 18th December by 10am. May her soul rest in peace!!!